MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This mapping is added as part of ITPR017177 - CV Rewrite Project. This process is to update the excpt_stat_cd on RCNT_RECN_PMT_CLM_LKUP to 'M' for the claims added as part of post-apc (which are manual claims). This mapping source the claims from RCNT_RECN_PMT_DSTR_DTL and gets the claims only when the txn_type_code is 'M'.
MAPPING.NAME: m_CASH_Update_RCNT_RECN_PMT_CLM_LKUP

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This mapping is added as part of ITPR017177 - CV Rewrite Project. This process is to update the excpt_stat_cd on RCNT_RECN_PMT_CLM_LKUP to 'M' for the claims added as part of post-apc (which are manual claims). This mapping source the claims from RCNT_RECN_PMT_DSTR_DTL and joins with the dstr_hdr, tperoid tables to gets the claims only when period, dstr_gid matches and txn_type_code is 'M'.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_RCNT_RECN_PMT_DSTR_DTL

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select distinct case when (substr(trim(TP.PERIOD_ID),1,1) = 'M') then TP.PERIOD_PARENT_ID else TP.PERIOD_ID END PRD_ID, PMT.CLM_GID from VRAP.RCNT_RECN_PMT_DSTR_DTL PMT, VRAP.TDISCNT_PERIOD TP, VRAP.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_HDR DSTR where DSTR.DSTR_STAT_CD = 15 and PMT.DSTR_GID = DSTR.DSTR_GID and TP.PERIOD_ID = DSTR.RBAT_BILL_PRD_NM and PMT.TXN_TYP_CD = 'M' with ur

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: hardcoded the excpt_stat_cd as 'M' for the manual claims.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: EXCPT_STAT

INSTANCE.DESCRIPTION: This mapping is added as part of ITPR017177 - CV Rewrite Project. This process is to update the excpt_stat_cd on RCNT_RECN_PMT_CLM_LKUP to 'M' for the claims added as part of post-apc (which are manual claims). This mapping source the claims from RCNT_RECN_PMT_DSTR_DTL and joins with the dstr_hdr, tperoid tables to gets the claims only when period, dstr_gid matches and txn_type_code is 'M'.
INSTANCE.NAME: SQ_RCNT_RECN_PMT_DSTR_DTL

SESSION.DESCRIPTION: This Sessios is added as part of ITPR017177 - CV Rewrite Project. This process is to update the excpt_stat_cd on RCNT_RECN_PMT_CLM_LKUP to 'M' for the claims added as part of post-apc (which are manual claims).
SESSION.NAME: s_m_CASH_Update_RCNT_RECN_PMT_CLM_LKUP

MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: Update the Distrubtion Header status to 15=Transmitting. If associated to a Snapshot, set the Snapshot Xmit Status to 15 also.
MAPPING.NAME: m_CASH_Update_Xmit_Status_Transmitting

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Build data for settting a Distribution Header to 15=Transmitting status.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_Dstr_Status

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Aggregate to one row per Snapshot
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: AGG_SnapIDs

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Build data for setting Snapshot Xmit Status to 15=Transmitting
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_Snap_Status

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: -- PARAMETERS used -- Get Snapshot of specific type that have NO distributions so we can set status to 15=Transmitting Select done per parameter file: CASH_Txn_Xmit_parm.txt
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_TSNAP

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select s.SNAP_ID from vrap.TSNAP s left join vrap.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_HDR d on d.DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD in ($$DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD) and d.DSTR_STAT_CD in ($$DSTR_STAT_CD) and d.PRCS_CRTE_ID = s.SNAP_ID where s.SNAP_APC_TYP_CD in ($$DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD) and s.SNAP_XMIT_STAT_CD in ($$DSTR_STAT_CD) and d.DSTR_GID is NULL

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: -- PARAMETERs used -- Get the Distribution Headers in a specific status and created by specific process(es). Select done per parameter file: CASH_Txn_Xmit_parm.txt
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_RCNT_RECN_DSTR_HDR

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Group: Distribution is all Distributions in 10=Ready to Stage status. These will be updated to 15=Transmitting. Group: Snapshot is Distrubtions from a Snapshot. Update the associated Snapshot status to 15=Transmitting.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: RTR_Headers

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1

GROUP.EXPRESSION:
IN(DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD, 1, 4, 5)
-- If this is a Snapshot, pass the SNAP_ID [in PRCS_CRTE_ID] to next transformation ---- 1=Pre-APC Snapshot ---- 4=APC Snapshot ---- 5=Post-APC Snapshot ---11=Outcome [do not pass these]
GROUP.NAME: SnapShot
